<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">为总结我校基层党组织工作经验，展示基层党支部和党员形象，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">12月6日下午，江西软件职业技术大学优秀主题党日活动案例评选在路演大厅举行。校党委书记、督导专员江延湖等校领导出席活动。党群部门负责人、各党总支书记及直属支部书记、党支部书记、组织员、党员代表等到场观赛。此次活动由校党委委员、组织部部长程杨胜主持。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-12-18%2009%3A34%3A43640.jpg?Expires=2018223283&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=WNk%2FEa%2FOa7vUdQT6tWMO%2B6juiQE%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">来自全校各基层党组织的</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">10支队伍在前期比赛中脱颖而出，角逐决赛。10位支部书记按抽签顺序依次上台分享案例。各个精彩案例的分享充分彰显了各党支部的战斗堡垒作用，为今后党日活动的灵活开展拓宽思路。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-12-18%2009%3A45%3A47DSC09868.JPG?Expires=2018223947&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=uEe41PHZ5Nk5Fw8QdiwD9KBpoMs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-12-18%2009%3A46%3A06DSC09895.JPG?Expires=2018223966&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=vpmQx0khRhv36ykhUNhJKssxxZI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">最终，网络工程学院教师党支部获得一等奖，区块链学院教师党支部、新媒体学院新媒体人通讯社党支部、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">VR与艺术学院学生党支部获得二等奖，信息技术学院学生党支部、智能科技学院学生党支部、经济管理学院学生党支部、马克思主义学院党支部、软件工程学院学生第二党支部获得三等奖，退役军人学院教师党支部获得优秀奖。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: basel